### Polymarket API Tests
### Используйте REST Client расширение для выполнения этих запросов

### ============================================
### Gamma API
### ============================================

### Get Events (Gamma API)
GET https://gamma-api.polymarket.com/events
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Event by Slug (GraphQL)
POST https://gamma-api.polymarket.com/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetEvent($slug: String!) { event(slug: $slug) { id title markets { id slug } } }",
  "variables": {
    "slug": "will-trump-win-2024-election"
  }
}

### ============================================
### HashDive API
### ============================================

### Get API Usage
GET https://hashdive.com/api/get_api_usage
x-api-key: {{HASHDIVE_API_KEY}}

### Get Trades
GET https://hashdive.com/api/get_trades?user_address={{WALLET_ADDRESS}}
x-api-key: {{HASHDIVE_API_KEY}}

### Get Positions
GET https://hashdive.com/api/get_positions?user_address={{WALLET_ADDRESS}}
x-api-key: {{HASHDIVE_API_KEY}}

### Get Latest Whale Trades
GET https://hashdive.com/api/get_latest_whale_trades?limit=10
x-api-key: {{HASHDIVE_API_KEY}}

### Search Markets
GET https://hashdive.com/api/search_markets?query={{SEARCH_QUERY}}
x-api-key: {{HASHDIVE_API_KEY}}

### ============================================
### Polymarket CLOB API
### ============================================

### Get Market by Condition ID
GET https://clob.polymarket.com/markets/{{CONDITION_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Market Prices
GET https://clob.polymarket.com/markets/{{CONDITION_ID}}/prices
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### Polymarket Analytics API
### ============================================

### Get Leaderboard (requires authentication)
GET https://polymarketanalytics.com/api/leaderboard
Content-Type: application/json

